<view class="page">
  <view class="checkout-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">计费</text>
    <view class="title">选择你需要的处理包</view>
    <view class="muted copy">支付前会明确包含内容、交付方式和退款规则。</view>
  </view>

  <view
    wx:for="{{products}}"
    wx:key="sku"
    class="card product-card {{selectedSku === item.sku ? 'selected' : ''}}"
    data-sku="{{item.sku}}"
    bindtap="select"
  >
    <view>
      <view class="product-name">{{item.name}}</view>
      <view class="muted product-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
    </view>
    <text class="product-price">{{item.price}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card limit-card">
    <view class="section-title">服务说明</view>
    <view class="limit-line">文书为辅助生成草稿。</view>
    <view class="limit-line">测算金额不保证最终赔偿结果。</view>
    <view class="limit-line">复杂案件可能需要人工复核。</view>
    <view class="limit-line">支付后会按服务进度适用退款规则。</view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-button" bindtap="pay">微信支付</button>
</view>

